		 threshold, which could be caused by excessive running vms using reserved hugepage memory. Possible
		 fix would be increasing page number of reserved hugepage memory or manually migrating
		 vms using reserved hugepage memory to other hosts."
	::= { h3cCasAlarmTrapPrefix 62 }

h3cCasAlarmHostDiskReadThroughputExceedThreshold NOTIFICATION-TYPE
